
<a name="ref_lib_align_center"></a>
<p class='bblib'><b><tt>[center]...[/center]</tt></b><br />
	The <tt>[center]</tt> tag causes its contents to be broken into a separate block and aligned horizontally
	to the center of the page.  Its end tag is required.</p>

<a name="ref_lib_align_left"></a>
<p class='bblib'><b><tt>[left]...[/left]</tt></b><br />
	The <tt>[left]</tt> tag causes its contents to be broken into a separate block and aligned horizontally
	to the left of the page.  Its end tag is required.</p>

<a name="ref_lib_align_right"></a>
<p class='bblib'><b><tt>[right]...[/right]</tt></b><br />
	The <tt>[right]</tt> tag causes its contents to be broken into a separate block and aligned horizontally
	to the right of the page.  Its end tag is required.</p>

<a name="ref_lib_align_indent"></a>
<p class='bblib'><b><tt>[indent]...[/indent]</tt></b><br />
	The <tt>[indent]</tt> tag causes its contents to be broken into a separate block and be to indented, to have
	an approximately half-inch margin on the left side.  Its end tag is required.</p>
